        <item>
            <title>YAMAHA 發佈電動電單車 MOTOROiD 2   加入 AI 技術實現自動駕駛目標</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/yamaha-motoroid2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=yamaha-motoroid2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/yamaha-motoroid2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 07:42:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199525</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本品牌 YAMAHA 近日發表新自體平衡電單車「MOTOROiD2」，並在其中引入 AI 技術，在上一代電單車的基礎上增強了人車互動的體驗感受。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1199542 aligncenter" style="text-align: center;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06-694x472.png" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06-694x472.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06-1280x871.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06-768x522.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06-1536x1045.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.06.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（圖片來源：<a href="https://global.yamaha-motor.com/showroom/event/japan-mobilityshow-2023/motoroid2/">global.yamaha-motor</a>）</p><p>MOTOROiD2 採用獨特的後搖臂設計以保持自立平衡，而其更新增了一組可動軸關節，讓車身後半部能夠與前半部獨立，朝向不同方向傾斜。</p><p>新車車身加強了流線造型設計，更取消了手把位置，換為在車頭兩側增設扶手。另外，MOTOROiD2 採用純電力推動，電池位於車身中央，摩打配置於後軸，外層有白色護罩搭配金色飾條。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25-694x511.png" alt="" width="694" height="511" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25-694x511.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25-1223x900.png 1223w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25-768x565.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25-1536x1130.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.25.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37-694x451.png" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37-694x451.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37-1280x832.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37-768x499.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37-1536x999.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.37.37.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34-694x472.png" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34-694x472.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34-1280x870.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34-768x522.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34-1536x1044.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.34.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41-694x503.png" alt="" width="694" height="503" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41-694x503.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41-1242x900.png 1242w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41-768x557.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41-1536x1113.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-15.00.41.png 1584w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-694x505.png" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-694x505.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-1236x900.png 1236w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-768x559.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-1536x1119.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1.png 1590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-694x536.png" alt="" width="694" height="536" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-694x536.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-1166x900.png 1166w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-768x593.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1.png 1480w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="https://global.yamaha-motor.com/showroom/event/japan-mobilityshow-2023/motoroid2/">global.yamaha-motor</a>）</p><p>而 YAMAHA 又開發了 AMCES 自動平衡制御系統，由人工智慧快速判斷車身狀態後不斷小幅出力，以保持車身自立不倒，實現電單車自動駕駛的目標。再者，車輛亦配有 AI 臉部與手勢辨識能力。</p><p>預計 YAMAHA 目前不會真正生產 MOTOROiD2 電動電單車，而該公司又指將在下個月於東京舉行的 2023 年日本移動展上展示 Motoroid 2 原型。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69124"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uH49vGi9_GA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2023/10/11/yamaha-motoroid-2-self-balancing-electric-motorcycle/">electrek</a>、<a href="https://global.yamaha-motor.com/showroom/event/japan-mobilityshow-2023/motoroid2/">global.yamaha-motor</a>、<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/tech/yamaha-driverless-motorbike-motoroid-2-b2427927.html">independent</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
