            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199422</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 2018 年以改編自 Marvel 英雄漫畫所推出的動作遊戲推出的《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman》其流暢動作遊戲玩法與開放式地圖大受好評，繼而在 2020 年推出續集外傳作品《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man: Miles Morales》來使用黑蜘蛛及特殊能力。直到 2023 年讓故事回到正傳，推出遊戲《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》讓前兩集主角再度攜手合作保護紐約家園的故事，正當大家期待新作品的時候然而這次感謝 PlayStation 提供的評測用遊戲可以優先為 Unwire 讀者進行評測。《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》於 2023 年 10 月 20 日正式發售，並只有 Playstation 5 平台才能遊玩。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199486 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲第二集畫面大幅提升</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲戰鬥方式也是改變不少</p><h2>面對現實與挑戰，雙主角的成長紀錄</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》的故事設定是上集《Miles Morales》的九個月後，渡過不少人生歷練之後終於回歸正常生活，但是世事豈能如常往往都有不同的危機，在雙主角互相重新審視自己的同時，一個接一個的強大反派都影響著兩位成為了成長的一部份。如果沒有遊玩前兩集的玩家也不用擔心遊戲會跟不上進度，也建議多花時間先觀看「劇情回顧」來對遊戲中的蜘蛛俠有一定認識。在遊戲整體的劇情都跟以往一樣十分流暢，如果是衝著劇情的部份玩家不用擔心，光是序章的部份就足以好比在看一場電影。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199496 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要面對現實的困難</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這次雙主角故事</p><h2>史詩式的對戰，強大的敵人登場</h2><p>要説到《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 》系列除了強大的遊戲劇情外，就是在遊戲中出現的強大敵人。而這次遊戲所鋪排出場的敵人，都是有著不同的個人特色霸氣登場，而登場的敵人除了曾在 Trailer 出現的幾個敵人外，還有更多極具危險的敵人潛伏著等待玩家大駕光臨。在遊戲中每個敵人登場都會給玩家一大挑戰，就像序章出現的沙人，所帶給紐約市的變化與及留下後續事件讓故事延續下去。隨著故事開放玩家定能體驗第 2 集所帶來的敵人，假若玩家有留意蜘蛛俠漫畫一定能體驗遊戲帶來的誠意。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199490 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Trailer 出現過的蜥蜴人</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲序章沙人就充滿驚喜</p><h2>更大的地圖，更多的任務</h2><p>比較於前作地圖只有紐約曼哈頓島之外，《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》還加入東河彼岸的布魯克林區與皇后區，相比前作差不多大了兩倍，而且區域之間地方差異大玩家會體驗當中的文化。那當然地圖也是採用開放式無縫地圖，而越大的地圖就有更多的任務等著玩家挑戰，像上集一樣除了會有觸發任務外，也可以掃描附近區域來取得資訊，今集更有著另一個功能「友善的鄰家蜘蛛人 APP」，玩家可以接受隨機任務完成後來獲得經驗值。值得注意與上集相若也是需要完成一些謎題才能開放區域，所以玩家可以優先先打開地圖。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199484 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今集地圖超大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遊戲中時代廣場</p><h2>拳拳到肉的表現，動作流暢極佳</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》保留了最原始最心動的動作效果，假若有遊玩以前作品的玩家在操作上必定能很快上手，射蜘蛛網，輕攻擊，閃避等等的操作仍然是一樣的，如沒玩過的玩家也只需要按著教學慢慢操作即可。今集玩家可以在雙角色間切換操作，使用超能力的黑蜘蛛特效上會比較浮誇一點，而蜘蛛俠則是以物理一拳拳運用戰衣打倒敵人，在戰鬥其間更有著慢動作與及各種動畫的配合，使得戰鬥更流暢更刺激。今集也會大玩合作攻擊，當然效果如何就等玩家自行慢慢發掘。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199492 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遊戲動作流暢度很高</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199487" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這次還有聯合攻擊</p><h2>重新設計的戰鬥系統，平衡戰鬥恰到好處</h2><p>這次《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》更改了不少的戰鬥系統，首先是不能再像以往一樣所有攻擊僅靠著迴避功能去躲開敵人攻擊，而是新增了另一種重攻擊需要利用新功能「擋格」再化解攻擊，這樣玩家就要更留意敵人的變化採取措施。而另一方面蜘蛛俠的特殊技能再不是透過技能樹或者連技使用出來，而是隨著遊戲進度裝備技能只需透過 L1 加上右邊四鍵使出強力攻擊，不過這些技能都是有冷卻時間，所以在運用的部份還是多多注意。這樣變了戰鬥過程不會因技能太強大而草草了事，玩家就可以專心動作的部份。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199481 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲技能都會有冷卻時間</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遊戲戰鬥平衡</p><h2>效能最佳化，讓遊戲推上另一個高度</h2><p>作為 Sony 旗下大作當然將遊戲在 PS5 下發揮至最大效能，除了畫質幾乎是極限表現外，還有手製的觸覺回饋，在不同環境下會有不同的震動與壓力讓玩家更有感覺。而遊戲支援 Tempest 3D AudioTech 功能，假若有比較好的耳機或家庭音響記得感受一下那種澎湃的臨場感覺。不論在畫面上甚至是蜘蛛俠衣的細緻位，在 SSD 下都能體驗到真實又快速的冒險。值得一提的是《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》除了支援 HDR 與圖形模式外，還支援了 120hz 及 VRR 「無上限」功能，對於擁有高階電視的玩家在遊戲下就更爽了。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199483 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲提起 120hz 跟 VRR</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲擁有高階電視的玩家有更好的體驗</p><h2>總結：絕對是今年最佳年度遊戲名單之一</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》將真正次世代的畫面與效能帶出來的作品，在實際遊玩的時候從畫面完全感受到所帶來的超美質感，在建築物上或者一些特效火花上都有著超高水準的顯示。其故事所傳遞的方式有深度又有意議，而且有遊戲中的影片與真實遊戲的運鏡真的是超驚歎作品的完成度。光在紐約擺盪滑翔在城市就能體驗鄰居蜘蛛俠的生活。在如此高水準的作品下作為喜歡 Marvel 或是動作遊戲的玩家，是值得推薦衝首發來支持一下。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199482 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲序章就可以體驗遊戲效能</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今集亦有技能樹系統</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這次亦有多款戰衣</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Venom 成為遊戲一大關鍵</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
